<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>AI Operations Dashboard</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Outfit:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f1f5f9 0%, #e2e8f0 100%);
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            color: #1e293b;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            min-height: 100vh;
        }

        header {
            width: 100%;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 3rem 0 2rem 0;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px -1px rgb(0 0 0 / 0.05);
            border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
            margin-bottom: 3rem;
        }

        header h1 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            margin: 0 0 0.5rem 0;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1e3a8a 0%, #3b82f6 100%);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
        }

        header p {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            color: #64748b;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        .dashboard-container {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(320px, 1fr));
            gap: 2rem;
            width: 90%;
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin-bottom: 4rem;
        }

        .module-card {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);
            backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
            border-radius: 16px;
            padding: 2.5rem 2rem;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 25px -5px rgb(0 0 0 / 0.1), 0 8px 10px -6px rgb(0 0 0 / 0.1);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            transition: all 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .module-card::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            height: 4px;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #e2e8f0, #cbd5e1);
        }

        .module-card.active::before {
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #3b82f6, #8b5cf6);
        }

        .module-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            box-shadow: 0 20px 25px -5px rgb(0 0 0 / 0.1), 0 10px 10px -5px rgb(0 0 0 / 0.04);
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
        }

        .module-icon {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            background: #eff6ff;
            width: 60px;
            height: 60px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            border-radius: 12px;
            color: #3b82f6;
        }

        .module-title {
            font-size: 1.25rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin: 0 0 1rem 0;
            color: #0f172a;
        }

        .module-desc {
            color: #475569;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            line-height: 1.5;
            flex-grow: 1;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
        }

        .module-features {
            list-style: none;
            padding: 0;
            margin: 0 0 2rem 0;
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            color: #64748b;
        }

        .module-features li {
            position: relative;
            padding-left: 1.2rem;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }

        .module-features li::before {
            content: '•';
            color: #3b82f6;
            position: absolute;
            left: 0;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .cta-button {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 0.875rem;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-size: 1rem;
            font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif;
            font-weight: 600;
            text-align: center;
            text-decoration: none;
            color: #fff;
            background: #cbd5e1;
            cursor: not-allowed;
            transition: all 0.3s;
            display: inline-block;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        .module-card.active .cta-button {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #3b82f6 0%, #2563eb 100%);
            cursor: pointer;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px -1px rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.3);
        }

        .module-card.active .cta-button:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 10px 15px -3px rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.4);
        }

        .badge {
            position: absolute;
            top: 1.5rem;
            right: 1.5rem;
            background: #dbeafe;
            color: #1e40af;
            font-size: 0.7rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            padding: 0.25rem 0.75rem;
            border-radius: 999px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
        }

        .badge.upcoming {
            background: #f1f5f9;
            color: #64748b;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <header>
        <h1>AI Operations Platform</h1>
        <p>Select a module to automate your workflows using specialized Gemini models and smart AI pipelines.</p>
    </header>

    <main class="dashboard-container">

        <!-- Module 1: AI Auto-Category & Tag Generator -->
        <div class="module-card active">
            <span class="badge">Active</span>
            <div class="module-icon">🏷️</div>
            <h2 class="module-title">AI Auto-Category & Tag Generator</h2>
            <p class="module-desc">Instantly analyze product images to structure catalog metadata cleanly for your
                database.</p>
            <ul class="module-features">
                <li>Auto-assign primary category</li>
                <li>Suggest sub-category</li>
                <li>Generate 5–10 SEO tags</li>
                <li>Suggest sustainability filters</li>
                <li>Deliver structured JSON output</li>
            </ul>
            <a href="/upload" class="cta-button">Launch Generator</a>
        </div>

        <!-- Module 2: AI B2B Proposal Generator -->
        <div class="module-card active">
            <span class="badge">Active</span>
            <div class="module-icon">📄</div>
            <h2 class="module-title">AI B2B Proposal Generator</h2>
            <p class="module-desc">Automatically craft B2B proposals optimized for budget constraints and impact
                metrics.</p>
            <ul class="module-features">
                <li>Suggest sustainable product mix</li>
                <li>Calculate budget allocation</li>
                <li>Estimate cost breakdown</li>
                <li>Summarize impact positioning</li>
                <li>Deliver structured JSON output</li>
            </ul>
            <a href="/proposal" class="cta-button">Launch Generator</a>
        </div>

        <!-- Module 3: AI Impact Reporting Generator -->
        <div class="module-card">
            <span class="badge upcoming">Coming Soon</span>
            <div class="module-icon">🌱</div>
            <h2 class="module-title">AI Impact Reporting Generator</h2>
            <p class="module-desc">Generate intelligent, human-readable impact reports based on order and product
                analysis.</p>
            <ul class="module-features">
                <li>Estimate plastic saved</li>
                <li>Calculate carbon avoided</li>
                <li>Summarize local sourcing impact</li>
                <li>Generate human impact statement</li>
            </ul>
            <a href="#" class="cta-button">Locked for Development</a>
        </div>

        <!-- Module 4: AI WhatsApp Support Bot -->
        <div class="module-card">
            <span class="badge upcoming">Coming Soon</span>
            <div class="module-icon">💬</div>
            <h2 class="module-title">AI WhatsApp Support Bot</h2>
            <p class="module-desc">Automate customer support using real-time database queries and escalation logic.</p>
            <ul class="module-features">
                <li>Answer order status queries</li>
                <li>Handle return policy questions</li>
                <li>Escalate high-priority issues</li>
                <li>Log conversations to database</li>
            </ul>
            <a href="#" class="cta-button">Locked for Development</a>
        </div>

    </main>
</body>

</html>